    <div class="project">
      <h2>A Simple Idea That Saves Lives</h2>
      <p>To address the rising issue of high-speed trains colliding with stray cattle, Wallenc developed a wearable safety band for livestock. This non-invasive band gently alerts animals as they near danger zones, helping them move away and avoid accidents.</p>
      <div class="impact">
        <h4>The Impact:</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Prevents cattle-train accidents</li>
          <li>Reduces railway disruptions</li>
          <li>Protects rural livestock</li>
          <li>Supports safer rail operations</li>
          <li>Backed by public awareness and field-tested success</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
      <h2>Invisible, Yet Unmistakable: Anti-Fraud Tech</h2>
      <p>Wallenc created a Water Soluble Anti-Counterfeiting Film to tackle return fraud in fashion and e-commerce. This invisible tag dissolves on use and reveals a secure code under UV light, ensuring product authenticity and preventing tampering.</p>
      <div class="impact">
        <h4>The Real-World Impact:</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Stops fraudulent returns and "wardrobing"</li>
          <li>Protects brand reputation</li>
          <li>Eco-friendly and product-safe</li>
          <li>Applicable across clothing, footwear, bags & more</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

